Create a survey fielding return

Create a survey fielding return

surveys_post_returns(survey_id, database_table_id = NULL,
  server_name = NULL, schema = NULL, table_name = NULL, metadata = NULL,
  status = NULL)

Arguments

survey_id

integer required. The ID of the survey.
database_table_id

integer optional. Table containing imported survey return
server_name

string optional.
schema

string optional.
table_name

string optional.
metadata

object optional.
status

string optional.

Value

A list containing the following elements:

id

integer, The ID of the return.

surveyId

integer, The ID of the survey.

fileId

integer, The ID of the file object.

s3Uri

string, URI of the S3 file

customImportJobId

integer,

databaseTableId

integer, Table containing imported survey return

metadata

object,

status

string,
